<p><a name="Important_settlements" id="Important_settlements"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mount_Athos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Important settlements">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Important settlements</span></h3>
